title: The Disney Princesses Work Out in 2017, and It's a Hilarious Disaster
text:
Blogilates Disney Princesses at the Gym Video The Disney Princesses Work Out in 2017, and It's a Hilarious Disaster January 3, 2017 by Dominique Astorino 27 Shares 
Get ready to watch your favorite Disney princesses sweat it out and make healthy New Year's resolutions: Blogilates star and trainer Cassey Ho wrote, directed, and starred in this silly and nostalgic comedy sketch. 
You'll instantly recognize the cast of familiar characters: Pocahontas, the earthy runner; Ariel, the boy-crazy . . . flailing mess; Jasmine, the bossy diva; Belle, the "beast mode" bookworm; and Aurora, who obviously overslept and barely made it to class. 
If you can't get enough of Disney-princess-themed exercise, you'll definitely want to try our Disney princess workout challenge . Related:
